      "rationale": "Analyst qualifications and simulation execution checklist are on file. Formal use-error study not required at MRL 2 per project requirements. Gradation 1 awareness level achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model form assumptions (turbulence model, hemolysis constitutive law) must be documented and their applicability to the COU argued.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published rotating-machinery benchmark studies. Giersiepen–Wurzinger hemolysis model applicability to CPB flow regimes documented with literature support. Achieved Gradation 2 exceeds MRL 2 project requirement of Gradation 1."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
