      "rationale": "Blood viscosity 0.0035 Pa·s, density 1060 kg/m³, pump geometry from FDA public dataset. Input parameter table documented in credibility assessment plan. Formal uncertainty propagation not required at MRL 2 per project requirements."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
