      "acceptanceCriteria": "Sample characterization for experimental validation data must be documented at awareness level.",
      "rationale": "FDA pump experimental data from publicly available interlaboratory study (5 laboratories). Sample characterization (bovine blood, hematocrit 35±2%) documented in source publication. Gradation 1 awareness level satisfies MRL 2 project requirements."
    },
