    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 with medium model influence per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH < 1 at all five operating points supports the submission decision. Project requirements are addressed in factor rationales throughout the assessment.",
